Botha front-end Employer view and an Admin Edit Job Listing view, same with Resumes and Company Profiles.

<img src="data:image/png;base64," />

The Create Job Posting function will need to find and reserve permission to display an active job posting from either the Credit or Subscription modules (should be extensible, allow plugging in modules). Admin can allow posting jobs for free in order to keep up volume on site.

All fields on the job posting need to be overridable, so that a job posting can be posted anonymously (without a company name).

Have an option to just clone an existing job posting, and edit it. Should give option to link to existing Candidate profile or create a new one, so old applications can be tied to the new posting if wanted.

Should have **workflow options** for creating job postings: allow a user to enter an ad, then notify someone at the company to approve it, and then that person has to approve it before it is billed and posted.

See notes in Job Categories file about UI for selecting job category.
